document_data.Interior:
The Palace was the best known example of [[Imaskari]] architecture. Its extra-dimensional spaces made it ten times bigger on the inside than on the outside, with many of them being used as vaults or arcane chambers.

The mind of Pandorym, an [[elder evil]], was held within the Imperial Weapons Cache.

By {{yearlink|1479}}, Ususi had moved the entire palace away from its original position, but its groundwork had remained behind. Thus, the original foundations and sublevels stayed now under the sand.{{cite book/Forgotten Realms Campaign Guide|224}}
